metadata.name: Where is Phone
metadata.description:
Where am I now ... I have no idea . It's so hot, Hey! where are my shoes how did i get here is that a cactus? I think I'm hallucinating because of the heat. anyway i need to get out of here... anyone around? I guess I'm the only one here... what is that ! a phone box. I hope it works because it looks very old. I need to reach it. The last thing I remember is falling asleep I hope it's a dream...
